pageContext.claim: “It is a Democrat Scam that is going nowhere but, future Presidents should in no way be compromised. What has happened to me should never happen to another President!”
pageContext.analysis: The impeachment process is part of the constitution. Trump frequently suggests what has happened to him is unique, but this impeachment concerns his handling of official acts as president. Bill Clinton was impeached for lying in a deposition about a private legal case.
